config APP_TETRIS
    bool "Tetris"
    default y
    depends on LIB_SEL4 && HAVE_LIBC && LIB_REFOS
    help
        Tetris game for RefOS. Drawing done using ANSI.
        The Tetris game is a demo for RefOS, showcasing UNIX-like dataspace
        printf, input functionality, and timer sleep functionality.
